(Note:  Double Punch is CLOAKED, though he has a FRINGE like effect.  For 
reference, watch Predator and see the Predator's cloak system, you'll see 
what I mean)

Punch/Double Punch/Breakdown/Hiss:



Punch, on a smashed tree, cursed, the log giving way and letting him plop to 
the ground weapons fire passing by him harmlessly.

Hiss ducked, a shot digging into his chest plate, sending him flying 
backwards.

Double Punch raised both pinchers, firing off an energy-signature seeking 
missile at Brooder's chest, and a missile at Hot Rod's left knee.

---

Breakdown cursed, firing off another grenade at Dinobot, soon the raptor was 
out of his sight.  "Slag.  Oh, well, I still whooped his scaly hide!" he 
yelled, firing off another grenade, blowing apart a large tree, the Predacon 
sitting down, firing off a grenade at the base of another tree.
